policies.title: Your Data
policies.text:
5 and its partners use cookies and similar technologies to store in your device to personalize your experience and be able to serve you with more relevant ‘targeted’ advertising.

For detailed information about how we use the data we store, you can read our privacy and cookie policies by clicking on the privacy policy link below.

To allow the use of your data to personalise your advertising and application experience click on ‘Accept all’. For full control of how we use your data click on edit settings and tell us what you’re happy with.
policies.dataText: We'd like to use the information you provide to us to personalise your 5 experience and deliver more relevant 'targeted' advertising. We will share your data to help make this experience a reality. – please let us know if you consent to the use of your data for this purpose.
policies.cookiesText: We’d like to store cookies on your device to be able to serve you with more relevant 'targeted' advertising – please let us know if you consent to the use of cookies for this purpose.

marketingConsentmodal.modalCopy: We'd love to keep in touch! Just let us know your preferences below.

marketingConsentmodal.viacomcbsText: Get exclusive, carefully-curated offers and promotions from our Paramount family of brands including MTV, Comedy Central and Paramount.
